^^^^^An intensive, naturalistic study tracked one six year old's learning for six months and more.  This document presents addition-related matter from the corpus of that study embedded in an interpretation.  The focus is on the learning processes through which a generally applicable  skill emerges from the integration of knowledge based on  specific, particular experiences.
