     The corpus of The Intimate Study is sufficiently rich in detail that I have been able to trace to a moment of insight Miriam's integration of formerly disparate microworlds.  We were on vacation at the time.  I felt Miriam had been working too hard at the laboratory and was determined that she should have a rest from our experiments.  I was curious, however, about the representation development of her finger counting and raised the question one day at lunch (@6;3;16):
